{"lemma":"قَطِيعٌ","slug":"قَطِيعٌ","root":"ق.ط.ع","root_slug":"ق-ط-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ط-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n42723"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"herd"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/qa.tˤiːʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n42723","headword_ar":"قَطِيعٌ","root":"qTE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A herd, troop, or drove; a distinct collection"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"number;"},{"kind":"text","text":"of beasts, &c.;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a flock,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bevy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of sheep, birds, &c.;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a party, or group, or collection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of men, &c.;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pack"},{"kind":"text","text":"of dogs. The term “ herd ” is applied to “ a collective number ” of camels by several good writers. We say a “ flock ” of sheep, and of geese; and “ herd ” or rather “ herd ” of goats; and a “ herd ” of oxen or kine, of camels, and of swine, and of antelopes; and a “ swarm ” of bees, &c. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTiyEN","text_ar":"قَطِيعٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A whip cut from the skin of a camel."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTiyEapN","text_ar":"قَطِيعَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion of land held in fee."},{"kind":"text","text":"See Mgh, Msb. ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quTiyEapN","text_ar":"قُطِيعَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hijoraAnN","text_ar":"هِجْرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTiyEapu","text_ar":"قَطِيعَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aHimi","text_ar":"الرَّحِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The cutting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forsaking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abandoning, of kindred,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relations; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Silapu Alr~aHimi","text_ar":"صِلَةُ الرَّحِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAliqapN","text_ar":"حَالِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}